Newpark Drilling Fluids provides drilling fluid products and technical services globally. Drilling projects involving complex subsurface conditions, such as horizontal, directional, or deepwater drilling require constant monitoring and critical engineering support.
Engineering support is provided from a technical team with years of experience solely focused on drilling fluids. As the largest, singularly-focused drilling fluids company in the world, Newpark’s attention to detail on technically complex wells is a step change from traditional bundled services providers. Teaming with Newpark means appropriate solutions while efficiently drilling in any environment.








