 Temporary Mats & Access Matting Solutions Menu

DURA-BASE® MatsDURA-BASE® Defender
Technical Information
T-REX™ Mat Cleaning SystemDURA-BASE® Advanced-Composite Mat System™EPZ Grounding System™







Newpark Mats & Integrated Services is the largest, most experienced manufacturer of heavy-duty advanced composite mat systems in the world. Our state-of-the-art, patented DURA-BASE® Advanced-Composite Mats are manufactured from high-performance thermoplastic into a single-piece construction that includes UV protection and static dissipation. The result is a mat system that is tough, field proven and reliable in even the most extreme environments. Our industry-leading products deliver custom engineered solutions for our customers that reduce costs, protect the environment and help ensure worker safety. 








