Newpark Resources, Inc.

2700 Research Forest Drive Suite 100 
The Woodlands TX 77381 United States
Phone: +1 281-___-____
Fax: +1 281-___-____
http://www.newpark.com





28
Managers




30
IT employees




$6.8MEST.
IT Budget




Newpark Resources, Inc. offers oil and gas exploration products and services. The company is split into three groups: Mats and Integrated Services, Environmental Services, and Fluids Systems and Engineering.
The IT department at Newpark Resources handles IT for all three business units at the company: Mats and Integrated Services, Environmental Services, and Fluids Systems and Engineering. The department spent much of 2010 and 2011 focusing on a new enterprise… MoreThe IT department at Newpark Resources handles IT for all three business units at the company: Mats and Integrated Services, Environmental Services, and Fluids Systems and Engineering. The department spent much of 2010 and 2011 focusing on a new enterprise resource planning (ERP) platform via Oracle. The enterprise business systems team oversaw the deployment.

The other key area for the department is the infrastructure group, a unit that includes networks and web development. This group was involved in a large-scale ERP rollout in 2011.

In spring 2011, the company started using @hand's mobile applications suite to allow teams to access information from the field.





